(43, 11, 24, 43, 5, 28, 29, 'resurrection at the last day', 'Resurrection Themes in John', 'This connection highlights the theme of resurrection present in both passages. Martha''s belief in the resurrection at the last day aligns with the promise of resurrection for all in John 5:28-29.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
